      • onReadyStateChange

        void onReadyStateChange(XMLHttpRequest2 xhr)
        This is called whenever the state of the XMLHttpRequest2 changes. See XMLHttpRequest2.setOnReadyStateChange(com.google.gwt.xhr2.client.ReadyStateChangeHandler).
        Parameters:
        xhr - the object whose state has changed.
